::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
Prestige |> 
    ggplot2::ggplot(
        ggplot2::aes(
            x = income,
            y = prestige
        )
    ) +
    ggplot2::geom_point(
        shape = "circle open",
        size = 2
    ) +
    ggplot2::stat_smooth(
        formula = 'y ~ x',
        method = "loess",
        span = .75,
        level = 0.95
    ) +
    ggplot2::stat_smooth(
        formula = 'y ~ x',
        method = "lm"
    ) +
    ggplot2::coord_cartesian(
      xlim = c(0, 26000),
      ylim = c(10, 90),
      expand = TRUE,
      default = FALSE,
      clip = "on"
)
```

